SORT: common sorting algorithms in C
====================================

COMPILE:
    make
    -> generates "libsort.a"

METHODS:
    #include "sort.h", then:
    void selectionSort(int arr[], int n);
    void bubbleSort(int arr[], int n);
    void insertionSort(int arr[], int n);
    void quickSort(int arr[], int n);
    void mergeSort(int arr[], int n);